N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9 ยง 4101.5 - Certificates of incorporation

State Regulations

Neither a certificate of incorporation under section
302 of the Racing, Pari-Mutuel Wagering and Breeding Law, nor a certificate of
amendment, shall be filed with the Secretary of State without the approval of
the commission or the commission's predecessor endorsed on or annexed to
it. Notes
